The pole shed has concrete floors with a 12-foot overhead door. The detached garage has a nice double overhead door plus a little extra space. The summer sleeping building is a flexible space to use anyway you like! The possibilities are endless, and the 1.3 acres of trees and shoreline won't disappoint.What I Love About The Home. This house is all about the lake! Views from every room on a huge 1.3 acre lot.

For sale: $269,900. Welcome home to this charming Mora hobby farm for sale just 5 minutes from town on 40 acres w/numerous outbuildings! Located within the Mora School District (ISD 332) not far from Ann Lake and the Ann Lake State Wildlife Management Area. This four bedroom, two bathroom Mora acreage property for sale features a spacious living room w/new flooring, windows allowing tons of natural light in, walkout to the concrete patio and a cutout view into the kitchen! The kitchen includes new stainless appliances, granite countertops, custom hickory cabinets, eat-in dining space and a spiral staircase that leads to the two upper level bedrooms! The main level of this Mora home for sale also includes two bedrooms, a full bathroom, a ¾ bathroom, breezeway from the garage to the home--great mudroom space and a main level laundry w/new front load washer/dryer. 

Additional amenities include solid oak panel doors, unfinished lower level, playhouse, outdoor spaces w/18x12 chicken coop, large 32x72 shed w/10ft overhead door and an 11ft sliding door on the side, 24ft lean-to, 32x48 detached garage/shed, tons of storage for farm equipment/animals, tillable/pasture/wooded land, fenced areas, large pond w/pasture area for natural watering and so much more!

Tons of potential to offer with this well maintained hobby farm for sale in Mora! Contact Chuck Carstensen with Re/Max Results at 612-290-3809 to setup your showing today!

description: For sale: $374,900. Great house on Fish Lake and the Ann River!  Features include an open floor plan with hardwood and ceramic tile floors, large master bedroom with an oversized walk in closet, full private master bathroom, finished walkout lower level to the lake, 6 car heated and insulated garage, 46 x 28 detached heated outbuilding for all the toys.  Located at the end of a quiet road with great views of the water on 6.4 acres with 900 ft of frontage.  Truly a must see home!

For sale: $239,900. Newly constructed beautiful home in a quiet, friendly, developed neighborhood. It is an on-slab home with easy to maintain stained concrete in-floor heated floors. It has 2 bedrooms, 1 and 1/2 baths and an open floor plan. The kitchen is large with custom knotty alder soft close cabinets, a 7ft center island including a snack bar and fingerprint resistant stainless steel Whirlpool appliances. The house also has a unique open air, screened, or enclosed sunroom/4 season with fireplace that over looks the back yard. This space is perfect for hosting back yard barbecues, enjoying the elements while watching the big game, or reading a good book. The living room, sunroom, and garage are all wired for sound and TV. All entry doors are setup for security cameras so that you can keep an eye on the place while you're away. The garage is finished with an 18 foot wide overhead insulated door and prepped for heat. There's additional storage in the attic over the garage accessible by a drop down ladder. This custom house was built using quality materials including Thermotech windows, Heritage solid core doors, Delta fixtures, and top of the line Mitsubishi mini split air conditioning system. No expense was spared to provide a quality home that's going to last.
